(1904, 151, 'title_0_subtext', 'Citrus Valley Physicians Group was founded in 1992 by Dr. C.K. Rao with the goal of creating a closely knit group of physicians dedicated to meeting the diverse need of patients and insurers in the East San Gabriel Valley.'),
