(1906, 151, 'title', '1'),
(1907, 151, '_title', 'field_5abc081df449b'),
(1908, 151, 'homepage_welcome_text_0_main_text', '<strong>Welcome to Citrus Valley Physicians Group</strong>'),
(1909, 151, '_homepage_welcome_text_0_main_text', 'field_5abc0832f449c'),
(1910, 151, 'homepage_welcome_text_0_subtext', 'Citrus Valley Physicians Group was founded in 1992 by Dr. C.K. Rao with the goal of creating a closely knit group of physicians dedicated to meeting the diverse need of patients and insurers in the East San Gabriel Valley. Since its inception CVPG has grown to a network of nearly 100 Primary Care Physicians and over 600 Specialists. \r\n<br>\r\nOur success is attributed to the quality physicians we contract with and the active role of our founder, Dr. Rao and his management team. Over the years our network has expanded into Montclair, Pomona, Glendale, San Fernando Valley, Long Beach, and Duarte. Our membership in our expansion areas has grown over 25%. We continue to grow within our original care network conveniently located in the San Gabriel Valley and surrounding cities.'),
